  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 5.1</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Check For</h1>\n  <p>An anti-virus solution should be deployed on all systems that are commonly targeted by malware.</p>\n  <h1>Why</h1>\n  <p>An anti-virus solution helps stop large-scale automated attacks.</p>\n  <h1>How to Check</h1>\n  <p>Identify all computers that use operating systems that are commonly affected by malware. Take a sample of these computers and verify that they have anti-virus software installed, if anti-virus software for these systems exists.</p>\n  <h1>How to Fix</h1>\n  <p>Identify all computers that use operating systems that are commonly affected by malware. Choose an anti-virus package that can be installed on these systems. When choosing an anti-virus package, consider the following capabilities:\n</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Automatic updates</li>\n    <li>Automatic scans</li>\n    <li>Log retention for at least a year</li>\n    <li>Ability to handle all known malware threat types</li>\n    <li>Integration with the centralized log server</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Install and configure the chosen anti-virus package on all the compatible systems.</p>\n  <h1>Related Items</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/article/6a12327a-3bc3-4acc-af65-9145046280b9\">Deploy an Anti-Virus</a>\n    </li>\n  </ul>"
